<title>Lead Like Robert E. Lee? No Way</title>
<description>
Robert E. Lee was a brilliant general. A great leader? No. He was a hypocrite and a traitor. Successful leadership requires acknowledging the facts, acting accordingly, and being true to your ideals.
</description>
